WEBVTT

00:00:26.539 --> 00:00:29.649
NOVEMBER FIVE, NINETEEN NINETY SIX.

00:00:29.649 --> 00:00:31.986
SHIMEN MENSHER. INTERVIEWER

00:00:31.986 --> 00:00:35.679
PHYLLIS DREAZEN. CHICAGO, ILLINOIS, U.S.A.

00:00:35.938 --> 00:00:37.569
YIDDISH ENGLISH.

00:00:39.567 --> 00:00:42.466
NOVEMBER FIVE, NINETEEN NINETY SIX.

00:00:42.466 --> 00:00:47.266
PHYLLIS DREAZEN INTERVIEWING SIMON MENTSHER, CHICAGO, ILLINOIS.

00:00:47.266 --> 00:00:49.449
WE'LL SPEAK IN YIDDISH AND ENGLISH.

00:00:50.856 --> 00:00:52.034
vi heystu?

00:00:52.257 --> 00:00:55.271
ikh heys Shimshen Mentsher ben Yosef.

00:00:56.998 --> 00:00:58.814
vi heystu in Amerike?

00:00:58.973 --> 00:01:01.498
in Amerike heys ikh SIMON Mentsher.

00:01:03.580 --> 00:01:05.453
un ven iz dayn geburtstog?

00:01:05.487 --> 00:01:08.535
mayn geburtstog iz may ELEVEN,

00:01:08.625 --> 00:01:10.441
toyznt nayn hundert tsvelef.

00:01:10.515 --> 00:01:12.436
un vi alt bistu yetst?

00:01:12.017 --> 00:01:13.648
ikh bin itstert alt

00:01:14.042 --> 00:01:16.753
akht, fir un akhtsik a helft.

00:01:17.306 --> 00:01:19.284
ver bistu geboyrn gevorn?

00:01:19.476 --> 00:01:23.655
ikh bin geboyrn gevorn dem eleftn may, nayntsn tsvelef.

00:01:23.323 --> 00:01:24.329
avu?

00:01:24.623 --> 00:01:27.081
in a dorf, Kosmatsh

00:01:27.238 --> 00:01:28.751
in di Karpatn,

00:01:29.348 --> 00:01:32.329
vu fun dem dorf iz shoyn mer keyn veg nisht gevezn.

00:01:32.385 --> 00:01:34.033
dos iz shoyn gevezn ende.

00:01:34.309 --> 00:01:37.728
vayl v- vayter iz shoyn geven grenets mit Rumenyen,

00:01:37.768 --> 00:01:39.905
mit Ungarn, Tshekhoslovakay.

00:01:40.266 --> 00:01:42.386
un s'iz geven groyse be- berg.

00:01:42.426 --> 00:01:45.693
keyn mashinen zenen nisht gevezn in yener tsayt,

00:01:45.818 --> 00:01:49.524
alts iz nor gevezn mit ferd oder tsu fus.

00:01:51.994 --> 00:01:53.304
a sheyn dorf,

00:01:53.428 --> 00:01:55.059
sheyne Karpatn.

00:01:54.812 --> 00:01:56.156
vifl mentshn?

00:01:56.247 --> 00:01:59.650
dort iz gevezn bay di zekhtsik mishpokhes yidishe.

00:02:00.195 --> 00:02:04.256
trots dem vos dos dorf iz gevezn shtark vayt fun a shtetele,

00:02:04.363 --> 00:02:06.095
ober di yidn hobn gehat

00:02:06.338 --> 00:02:08.256
yeder zayn arbet,

00:02:08.346 --> 00:02:11.445
yeder zayn baruf, basheftikung,

00:02:11.788 --> 00:02:13.233
un mentshn hobn gelebt.

00:02:13.257 --> 00:02:15.810
nisht lang, vayl Poyln iz antshtanen

00:02:15.810 --> 00:02:17.903
in toyznt nayn hundert tsvontsik.

00:02:17.903 --> 00:02:21.131
in toyznt nayn hundert nayn un draysik iz gevorn oys Poyln,

00:02:21.542 --> 00:02:23.561
iz in gantsn nayntsn yor.

00:02:23.972 --> 00:02:27.023
fun nayntsn tsvelef biz nayntsn tsvontsik

00:02:27.023 --> 00:02:30.379
iz dos gevezn nisht Poyln, iz dos gevezn AUSTRO-WĘGRY.

00:02:31.093 --> 00:02:33.804
in nayntsn tsvontsik iz dos gevorn Poyln,

00:02:33.861 --> 00:02:35.812
hot men es gerufn Kleyn-Poyln,

00:02:36.662 --> 00:02:38.529
oder Galitsyen,

00:02:38.923 --> 00:02:42.697
funem vort vayl s'iz geven a dorf Halitsh,

00:02:42.771 --> 00:02:46.168
un dort iz geven a a groyser mentsh, an ukrainer,

00:02:46.168 --> 00:02:49.531
hobn es di ukrainer gerufn HALICHINA

00:02:49.622 --> 00:02:51.973
un di estr-, austro-vengryer hobn gerufn

00:02:51.973 --> 00:02:53.159
GALIZIEN.

00:02:53.335 --> 00:02:57.041
un azoy iz dos gevorn in der yidisher shprakh, hot men gezogt "a galitsyaner".

00:02:57.621 --> 00:02:59.415
in Galitsyen geyt arayn:

00:02:59.415 --> 00:03:00.365
KRAKÓW,

00:03:00.523 --> 00:03:03.605
Tarnopol, Stanisloy un Lemberik.

00:03:03.966 --> 00:03:06.947
di fir voyevudstves zenen gevezn gerekhnt

00:03:07.003 --> 00:03:09.911
in Galitsyen. di iberike teyln fun Poyln

00:03:09.911 --> 00:03:11.722
zenen geven Tsentral-Poyln

00:03:11.914 --> 00:03:13.933
un andere teyln fun Poyln.

00:03:15.593 --> 00:03:18.827
dertseyl undz epes vegn dayn familye.

00:03:19.440 --> 00:03:21.965
ikh bin geboyrn ⟨in⟩ nayntsn tsvelef.

00:03:22.360 --> 00:03:24.601
in nayntsn fertsn hot zikh ongehoybn

00:03:24.601 --> 00:03:26.285
di ershte velt-milkhome.

00:03:26.342 --> 00:03:28.361
bin ikh alt geven tsvey yor.

00:03:29.025 --> 00:03:32.869
mayn tate iz nisht a profesyonaler, ah, rebe,

00:03:32.869 --> 00:03:34.638
ober er hot gehat smikhe.

00:03:34.847 --> 00:03:37.625
hot men im in nayntsn fertsn di estraykher

00:03:37.750 --> 00:03:40.764
mobilizirt in der armey als rebe.

00:03:41.496 --> 00:03:43.771
un in der tsayt

00:03:43.771 --> 00:03:46.906
hobn di rusn gehat a groysn nitsokhn,

00:03:47.233 --> 00:03:50.647
un di estraykhishe armey hot opgetretn

00:03:50.647 --> 00:03:54.349
fun ire grenetsn zenen zey ariber biz der tshekhisher teritorye.

00:03:54.928 --> 00:03:56.474
un dortn

00:03:56.599 --> 00:04:03.377
hobn zey, zet oys, oyfgehaltn a bisl di rusn, ober mayn tate iz shver farvundet gevorn,

00:04:03.433 --> 00:04:06.970
un in shpitol iz er geshtorbn.

00:04:07.804 --> 00:04:11.100
mir zenen geblibn n- in der heym.

00:04:11.100 --> 00:04:14.379
un s'iz ge-, ale mentshn hobn zikh evakuirt,

00:04:14.487 --> 00:04:17.636
⟨nor⟩ vayl s'iz geven zeyer groyse milkhomes dortn.

00:04:18.047 --> 00:04:21.011
iz mayn mame ge⟨shtonen iber der letster tsayt⟩

00:04:21.067 --> 00:04:28.447
mit a groysn kestl kakao, mit, mit bulkelekh, vayl di yidn fun di shtetl⟨ekh zenen gegangen⟩ durkh undzer dorf

00:04:28.447 --> 00:04:29.988
kedey tsu antloyfn

00:04:30.163 --> 00:04:33.971
un in letstn moment hot zi genemen oyf a vogn mit a ferd

00:04:34.146 --> 00:04:37.110
un hot undz ale arayngezetst. ⟨zenen mir damolts⟩ gevezn

00:04:37.521 --> 00:04:39.618
finef meydlekh,

00:04:39.618 --> 00:04:41.244
un ikh bin geven eyner.

00:04:41.301 --> 00:04:43.219
du vilst zogn di nemen?

00:04:42.668 --> 00:04:45.609
yo. se, akhuts mir iz gevezn,

00:04:45.609 --> 00:04:47.960
di eltste shvester iz gevezn Dine,

00:04:48.490 --> 00:04:50.880
un di tsveyte nokh ir iz geven Roze,

00:04:50.886 --> 00:04:53.141
di drite iz gevezn Ester,

00:04:53.248 --> 00:04:56.957
un di letste tsvey Maynkele un Sorkele.

00:04:56.826 --> 00:04:57.900
un di...

00:04:56.957 --> 00:05:01.258
mer-veyniker a yor ⟨UNK⟩rikht, ober ikh gedenk nisht genoy.

00:05:01.534 --> 00:05:04.346
un ikh bin geven der yingster.

00:05:03.897 --> 00:05:05.140
di mame?

00:05:05.230 --> 00:05:07.249
di mame Khane,

00:05:06.040 --> 00:05:07.611
hot gehey- Khane.

00:05:07.879 --> 00:05:12.540
di mame Khane. vi azoy iz mayn tate gekumen fun Tarnopoler voyevudstve

00:05:12.590 --> 00:05:14.490
keyn Stanislover in Karpatn,

00:05:14.490 --> 00:05:17.862
veys ikh nisht, vayl ikh bin dokh, ikh bin geven a kind.

00:05:17.869 --> 00:05:21.376
ober yedn fals, s'iz dray hundert kilometer a mehalekh

00:05:21.376 --> 00:05:23.837
fun dem ort vu mayn tate iz geboyrn gevorn.

00:05:24.062 --> 00:05:27.768
bay mayn mame's tsad iz gevezn nayn kinder,

00:05:28.011 --> 00:05:29.794
zin un tekhter.

00:05:29.952 --> 00:05:32.393
tate's tsad iz gevezn tsen,

00:05:32.787 --> 00:05:35.846
un ale zenen shoyn gevezn groyse,

00:05:35.846 --> 00:05:38.461
es iz shoyn gevezn fun di k- fun di kinder,

00:05:38.461 --> 00:05:41.133
fun di tekhter, fun di zin iz shoyn geven mishpokhes,

00:05:41.207 --> 00:05:42.883
un

00:05:42.883 --> 00:05:46.567
der tate hot gehat a groys hoyz oyfgeboyt.

00:05:46.911 --> 00:05:50.612
mit vos er hot zikh farnemen veys ikh nisht, nor mir hobn gehat zeyer a sakh

00:05:50.612 --> 00:05:51.968
shtiklekh feld.

00:05:52.294 --> 00:05:56.526
di Karpatn zenen dokh groyse berg. un dort vu s'iz do a shtikl glaykher plats,

00:05:56.526 --> 00:05:59.577
dort ken men boyen a hoyz oder farakern,

00:05:59.652 --> 00:06:03.578
vayl in Karpatn iz dos erd nisht keyn shvartse erd,

00:06:03.718 --> 00:06:05.652
nor s'iz gevezn

00:06:05.845 --> 00:06:08.134
 grintsayg,

00:06:08.207 --> 00:06:10.057
sades frukhtn.

00:06:10.705 --> 00:06:13.196
di ortshaft iz geven azoy sheyn,

00:06:13.422 --> 00:06:15.728
vayl s'iz gevezn bern,

00:06:16.273 --> 00:06:17.735
bure bern,

00:06:17.792 --> 00:06:21.144
velf iz zenen gantse stades ge- gevezn

00:06:21.167 --> 00:06:23.051
un vilde khazeyrim.

00:06:23.361 --> 00:06:27.678
un di p- di politsey di estraykhishe un di poylishe dernokh

00:06:27.678 --> 00:06:31.576
flegn trefn nor a shtikl in shikh, a shtikl fus.

00:06:31.576 --> 00:06:33.109
zey flegn iberfaln.

00:06:33.418 --> 00:06:38.272
un me hot nisht derloybt tsu m- tsu hargenen zey, tsu shi- tsu shisn,

00:06:38.363 --> 00:06:41.884
nor groyse mentshn hobn gekent yedes mol makhn

00:06:41.890 --> 00:06:45.039
polyevanye un un opshisn zey.

00:06:45.973 --> 00:06:48.279
di gegnt aleyn iz geven azoy sheyn,

00:06:48.420 --> 00:06:50.864
az a sakh mentshn hobn gezogt, az

00:06:50.864 --> 00:06:52.836
s'farglaykht zikh vi Shveytsaryen.

00:06:53.432 --> 00:06:55.130
un nisht gekukt deroyf

00:06:55.204 --> 00:06:57.934
vos di yidn zenen geven nisht keyn shtark raykhe,

00:06:57.934 --> 00:07:01.006
nor zey hobn gehat mer-veyniker di parnose: iz geven shusters,

00:07:01.006 --> 00:07:02.238
shnayders,

00:07:02.238 --> 00:07:03.604
zey hobn gehat gevelbn.

00:07:03.604 --> 00:07:06.329
un zeyer a sakh yidn hobn zikh take farnemen aleyn.

00:07:06.329 --> 00:07:07.967
zey hobn gehat gute sadn,

00:07:07.967 --> 00:07:10.337
un di frukhtn hobn zey gehat i zumer

00:07:10.337 --> 00:07:13.135
i osyen frukhtn un far vinter oykh.

00:07:13.378 --> 00:07:15.510
dermit flegn zey dos farkoyfn.

00:07:15.510 --> 00:07:18.286
itster flegn zey koyfn bay di ukrainer

00:07:18.286 --> 00:07:19.931
di beste gribes,

00:07:19.931 --> 00:07:21.542
MUSHROOMS.

00:07:21.542 --> 00:07:23.669
vayse, on eyn vorem

00:07:23.669 --> 00:07:26.538
iz ge-, flegn trikenen, zeyer fayne.

00:07:26.538 --> 00:07:29.471
flegn dos zeyer gut koyfn di groyse shtet,

00:07:29.578 --> 00:07:32.322
Varshe un Lodzh un Lemberik.

00:07:32.532 --> 00:07:36.660
itstert-o, ze-, di goyim flegn trikenen di frukhtn,

00:07:36.801 --> 00:07:39.244
un zey flegn es makhn zeyer sheyn un reyn.

00:07:39.244 --> 00:07:41.953
akhuts dem iz geven in der gegnt zeyer a sakh

00:07:41.953 --> 00:07:43.257
yagedes,

00:07:43.517 --> 00:07:45.927
dos heyst mali- malines,

00:07:45.927 --> 00:07:48.877
CHERNIKA, di... ofenes.

00:07:49.018 --> 00:07:53.225
un dos alts fleg men mit azelkhe feser

00:07:53.225 --> 00:07:54.297
hiltserne

00:07:54.297 --> 00:08:00.662
onlodn oyf a ferd tsvey feser azelkhe, un raytndik mitn ferd, vayl s'iz

00:08:00.662 --> 00:08:05.271
nisht gevezn keyn guter veg. nokh yedn regn iz der veg gevorn tse- tseveykt.

00:08:05.826 --> 00:08:10.792
di, di, di velder dortn zenen gevezn zeyer gute kvalitet.

00:08:10.792 --> 00:08:12.353
say di sosnes,

00:08:12.353 --> 00:08:13.784
say di bereze,

00:08:13.960 --> 00:08:15.591
say buk,

00:08:15.681 --> 00:08:16.957
say dub,

00:08:17.284 --> 00:08:22.104
un di beste avyos, avyo-beryozn, avyo-sosne.

00:08:22.144 --> 00:08:25.018
fleg men nisht megn hakn

00:08:25.018 --> 00:08:27.250
on der erloybenish funem LEŚNICZY.

00:08:27.392 --> 00:08:30.778
oyb der LEŚNICZY hot erloybt, hot men gemegt oyshakn a bisl f-

00:08:30.801 --> 00:08:33.514
beymer kedey makhn a remont funem hoyz.

00:08:33.514 --> 00:08:36.667
ober on an erloybenish hot men gornisht getort t- tun.

00:08:38.125 --> 00:08:42.500
akhuts dem iz di mentshn,

00:08:42.500 --> 00:08:45.847
zey hobn, zenen gevezn zeyer, di yidn,

00:08:45.887 --> 00:08:47.585
frayndlekh tsu zikh.

00:08:47.710 --> 00:08:54.015
un khotsh dos dorf iz gevezn tsevorfn, fun a hoyz biz a hoyz iz geven hundert un tsvey hundert meter a mol,

00:08:54.190 --> 00:08:56.918
nor di, iz geven tsvey shiln.

00:08:57.430 --> 00:09:00.683
un, s'iz nisht geven ⟨a⟩ shnayder-shil oder

00:09:00.683 --> 00:09:04.185
oder andere oder a kloyz epes, proste shiln, vi in a dorf,

00:09:04.185 --> 00:09:06.013
oysgeboyt fun holts.

00:09:06.120 --> 00:09:09.180
in dorf iz gevezn di melamdim,

00:09:09.180 --> 00:09:13.348
vos hobn gelernt dem tsu ershtn dem alef-beys

00:09:13.348 --> 00:09:14.740
un dernokh davenen.

00:09:14.740 --> 00:09:18.990
un a a bisl hot men ongehoybn tsu lernen shoyn afile khumesh un Rashe.

00:09:19.063 --> 00:09:22.528
un, nor di ale yidn, trots dem

00:09:22.528 --> 00:09:25.976
vos zey zenen geven draysik-fertsik kilometer fun a shtetele,

00:09:26.067 --> 00:09:29.886
un keyn beys-oylem iz nisht gevezn dortn. flegn, az se fleg shtarbn a yid,

00:09:29.886 --> 00:09:31.767
fleg men firn mit a vogn

00:09:31.767 --> 00:09:34.492
tsvelf kilometer, fuftsn kilometer.

00:09:34.492 --> 00:09:36.911
tsvey kilometer, dakht zikh mir, iz a mayl.

00:09:37.390 --> 00:09:42.564
un di un di yidn zenen gevezn genug baleznt.

00:09:42.705 --> 00:09:46.768
in Poyln, iz afile in aza min dorf farvarfn,

00:09:46.768 --> 00:09:49.195
iz gevezn a Tarbut-shul

00:09:49.607 --> 00:09:51.069
un a yidishe shul,

00:09:51.396 --> 00:09:53.094
un der melamed hot gelernt.

00:09:53.168 --> 00:09:56.587
di eltern vos zey zenen gevezn farmeglekh flegn shikn di kinder

00:09:56.678 --> 00:09:59.794
in in shtetlekh oder in shtet.

00:10:00.154 --> 00:10:02.476
di noentste shtot iz gevezn Kolomey.

00:10:02.483 --> 00:10:07.711
di hoyptshtot iz gevezn, di di oblast, di voyevudstve iz geven Stanisloy.

00:10:07.711 --> 00:10:10.166
nor Kolomey iz gevezn merer

00:10:10.166 --> 00:10:17.006
merer mit miskher, vayl s'iz gevezn, fun Kolomey keyn Stanisloy iz geven zeyer vayt.

00:10:17.080 --> 00:10:19.084
flegn kumen di hutsuln,

00:10:19.084 --> 00:10:21.089
di ukrainer hot men gerufn di hutsuln.

00:10:21.197 --> 00:10:22.518
flegn kumen

00:10:22.518 --> 00:10:25.185
ahin un ⟨UNK⟩ ⟨oysfar⟩koyfn, azoy

00:10:25.185 --> 00:10:28.143
der groyser miskher tsvishn yidn fun di derfer.

00:10:28.200 --> 00:10:30.939
geven etlekhe un draysik derfer leng-oys

00:10:30.939 --> 00:10:34.016
der rumenisher, tshekhisher un ungerisher grenets.

00:10:34.748 --> 00:10:39.427
s'iz nisht keyn fele, az yidn zol zikh mishn mit andere felker.

00:10:39.427 --> 00:10:41.545
yidn mit yidn hobn khasene gehat.

00:10:41.545 --> 00:10:44.124
moral iz gevezn genug hoykh.

00:10:44.383 --> 00:10:47.679
un s'iz geven yidishe organizatsyes.

00:10:47.679 --> 00:10:53.067
nor in di derfer flegn zayn merstn teyl stam sionistishe organizatsyes.

00:10:53.091 --> 00:10:54.936
HANOAR HATSIYONI,

00:10:54.936 --> 00:10:57.914
ober nisht di linke. geven HASHOMER HATSAIR,

00:10:57.914 --> 00:11:00.577
linke Poletsiyen, rekhte Poletsiyen,

00:11:00.600 --> 00:11:03.614
di GORDONIA, di iberike, dos iz shoyn geven ⟨in⟩ di shtetlekh.

00:11:04.937 --> 00:11:06.703
MIZRAKHI gevezn, yo.

00:11:06.642 --> 00:11:07.749
BEITAR?

00:11:07.468 --> 00:11:11.697
a sakh yidn in dorf hobn ge- zaynen geven groyse la- lamdonim, zey hobn gelernt.

00:11:11.721 --> 00:11:15.658
zey hobn gehat a sakh beheymes. flegn zey geyn mit beheymes pasn zey

00:11:15.658 --> 00:11:17.717
un zitsn mit a gemore lernen.

00:11:17.717 --> 00:11:21.573
es flegt zikh afile makhn, az zeyere behemeys flegn arayngeyn in a fremdn gortn,

00:11:21.573 --> 00:11:23.766
un makhn a shodn bay di ukrainer.

00:11:23.766 --> 00:11:26.415
iz er gekumen tsu geyn un hot geshrign: ⟨vos iz es?⟩ ⟨gezogt im⟩ sha!

00:11:26.415 --> 00:11:28.269
shray nisht, ikh vel dir batsoln.

00:11:28.528 --> 00:11:31.765
un hot vayter gelernt, un der, di ki zenen vayter gegangen

00:11:31.765 --> 00:11:33.669
un hobn getun shodns.

00:11:33.895 --> 00:11:36.808
af yedn fals, biz nayntsn nayn un draysik

00:11:36.865 --> 00:11:43.541
iz dos yidntum in Poyln, kimat fir milyon, genoy veys ikh nisht, nor s'iz mistome dray milyon akht hundert toyznt,

00:11:43.750 --> 00:11:48.522
zenen gevezn rekrutirt in ale, nisht nor in Galitsyen,

00:11:48.522 --> 00:11:50.176
in Tsentral-Poyln,

00:11:50.176 --> 00:11:53.902
zenen in di kleyne shtetlekh, in di derfer geven umetum yidn.

00:11:54.043 --> 00:11:56.349
nor dort, vu se geven gute felder

00:11:56.423 --> 00:11:58.324
un gute erd,

00:11:58.363 --> 00:12:01.901
dort hobn di yidn zikh take farnumen mit landvirtshaft.

00:12:01.924 --> 00:12:05.276
un zey zaynen gevezn nit erger bahavnt in der arbet

00:12:05.333 --> 00:12:11.480
vi di ukrainer oder vi di polyakn. tsum bayshpil, Tarnopoler voyevudtsve, vu mayn tate iz geboyrn gevorn,

00:12:11.480 --> 00:12:14.321
dort iz gevezn di beste erd in Poyln.

00:12:14.665 --> 00:12:18.104
dort hot men yede zibn-akht yor badarft gebn a bisl

00:12:18.104 --> 00:12:20.567
vi- badinung, dos heyst

00:12:20.567 --> 00:12:22.457
fun di beheymes, fun di ferd,

00:12:22.457 --> 00:12:25.290
kedey dos feld zol vern beser.

00:12:26.629 --> 00:12:30.605
azoy arum hob ikh geendikt tsvey klasn mistam.

00:12:30.662 --> 00:12:34.065
az-, vayl nayntsn akhtsn iz geshtorbn mayn mame.

00:12:34.197 --> 00:12:36.150
bin ikh alt gevezn zeks zeks yor.

00:12:36.143 --> 00:12:37.248
fun vos?

00:12:37.210 --> 00:12:39.347
zi, geshtorbn, zi

00:12:39.387 --> 00:12:41.811
⟨ot⟩ mir hobn gehat zeks beheymes.

00:12:41.884 --> 00:12:49.845
un zi hot z- zikh dershvitst gevorn, un dos vaser in di Karpatn iz gevezn zumer in der grester hits

00:12:49.845 --> 00:12:51.288
azoy kalt

00:12:51.288 --> 00:12:52.881
un azoy min frish.

00:12:53.157 --> 00:12:57.150
hot zi ongetrunken zikh mit kalt vaser, hot bakumen a lungen-tsindung,

00:12:57.342 --> 00:13:01.852
un ven s'iz do a dokter oder oder a kranken-shvester,

00:13:01.852 --> 00:13:03.984
⟨nu⟩ volt men zi gekent rateven.

00:13:04.007 --> 00:13:07.489
zi iz prost ⟨un⟩ poshet in fir un tsvantsik sho farbrent gevorn.

00:13:07.489 --> 00:13:09.952
nisht gekukt deroyf vos in dorf iz gevezn

00:13:09.952 --> 00:13:12.034
shvester un brider fun der mame.

00:13:12.225 --> 00:13:17.636
ge- ge- a sakh, vayl e- etlekhe hobn gevoynt nisht inem dorf, ⟨nor⟩ shoyn in di shtet.

00:13:17.693 --> 00:13:20.069
ober in dorf iz oykh geven fir-finef

00:13:20.069 --> 00:13:24.009
shvester un brider. der eltster bruder fun der mame iz geven dortn.

00:13:24.009 --> 00:13:26.799
ober biz zey zenen gekumen, iz zi shoyn geven toyt.

00:13:27.278 --> 00:13:30.765
un mir hobn zi gefirt akhtsn kilometer in a dorf Pistin.

00:13:30.789 --> 00:13:36.090
gedenkstu epes fun di ershte zeks yorn?

00:13:36.120 --> 00:13:39.593
ikh gedenk fun di ershte zeks yorn

00:13:39.613 --> 00:13:43.727
ven di mame iz geshtorbn, hot mir gezogt di eltste shvester Dine:

00:13:43.727 --> 00:13:47.069
Shimshele, gey ruf Rozen, di mame ⟨iz⟩ geshtorbn

00:13:47.069 --> 00:13:50.562
bin ikh vi a ge-, vi a vilder bokher gelofn, shray: Roze!

00:13:50.562 --> 00:13:52.646
kum aheym, di mame iz geshtorbn.

00:13:52.646 --> 00:13:59.283
ikh gedenk di shkotsim, vos zenen gegangen mit mir in shul. vayl mir zenen gegangen tsvey kilometer, mit a, a zekl oyf di pleytses.

00:13:59.307 --> 00:14:07.536
vayl di shul iz gevezn in tsentraln teyl. dos dorf iz gevezn efsher dray kilometer tsevorfn. vayl di gebirg- berg.

00:14:07.828 --> 00:14:09.290
gedenk ikh zey.

00:14:09.718 --> 00:14:12.921
hob ikh afile gehat aza min fal. ven ikh bin gevezn in Sibir,

00:14:12.921 --> 00:14:15.250
hot men gebrakht tsu firn a nayem etap.

00:14:15.250 --> 00:14:17.039
un s'iz ongekumen a hoykher

00:14:17.039 --> 00:14:19.149
sheygets.

00:14:19.149 --> 00:14:23.010
un ikh hob derkent im, ⟨UNK⟩ dos iz ⟨UNK⟩ vos er ⟨iz gegan mit⟩ mir in shul.

00:14:23.286 --> 00:14:26.908
un azoy vi er iz beshas der okupatsye geven in dem dorf,

00:14:26.965 --> 00:14:29.839
vu ma-, vi s'iz geboyrn gevorn mayn mame,

00:14:29.839 --> 00:14:32.257
hob ikh im gefregt: host a sakh yidn geharget?

00:14:32.297 --> 00:14:35.666
hot er geshtelt oyf di kni un ⟨hot⟩ gezogt: ikh hob keynem nisht geharget.

00:14:35.925 --> 00:14:38.602
vayl biz nayntsn nayn un draysik

00:14:38.710 --> 00:14:40.560
fle- ⟨zenen⟩ mir gevezn kinder,

00:14:40.633 --> 00:14:42.854
di shtub iz nisht geven farmakht,

00:14:42.912 --> 00:14:45.724
di goyim zaynen gegangen shiker, zey hobn emetsn nisht gerirt.

00:14:46.236 --> 00:14:48.890
un bikhlal gedenk ikh nisht, in azoy fil,

00:14:48.890 --> 00:14:50.544
tsener defer

00:14:50.544 --> 00:14:52.321
zol zayn a fal

00:14:52.446 --> 00:14:56.068
⟨ven⟩ zeyer zeyer veynik iz geven faln, vos m'hot baroybt.

00:14:56.580 --> 00:14:58.649
m'hot gelebt tsuzamen,

00:14:58.842 --> 00:15:02.953
zey hobn gelign gelt, zey hobn opgegebn gelt, m'hot gefirt a miskher,

00:15:03.027 --> 00:15:07.596
un di yidn hobn zikh bamit tsu lebn azoy min frayndlekh mit zey,

00:15:07.596 --> 00:15:10.040
zey hobn nisht gehat keyn sibe dertsu,

00:15:10.047 --> 00:15:11.863
az zoln zayn sonim.

00:15:11.680 --> 00:15:13.460
un keyn antisemitizm?

00:15:13.260 --> 00:15:16.858
mitn kumen tsu der makht fun Hitlern ⟨in⟩ nayntsn dray un draysik...

00:15:16.870 --> 00:15:17.700
ober far?

00:15:18.045 --> 00:15:19.760
far Hitlern

00:15:20.205 --> 00:15:24.485
di ikh gedenk nisht, ikh gedenk nisht.

00:15:24.492 --> 00:15:28.350
nor ikh meyn, az der antisemitizm, oyb er iz gevezn,

00:15:28.710 --> 00:15:31.319
iz dos, iz er gegan tomed funem kloyster,

00:15:31.427 --> 00:15:33.108
funem galekh.

00:15:33.638 --> 00:15:37.440
di galokhim, spetsyel bay undz, zaynen nisht geven azoy aktiv

00:15:37.440 --> 00:15:39.642
in der propagande fun antisemitizm.

00:15:39.642 --> 00:15:43.082
in Tsentral-Poyln, di po- di poylishe zaynen geven shreklekh.

00:15:43.105 --> 00:15:46.477
fun zey iz aroysgekumen alts, ⟨az⟩ di yidn hobn ge-

00:15:46.477 --> 00:15:50.163
gehongen dem Yezus Kristus,

00:15:50.163 --> 00:15:51.417
dos Yoyzl.

00:15:51.508 --> 00:15:55.648
un bay undz, farshteyt zikh, iz gevezn. me ken nisht zogn, az nisht,

00:15:55.648 --> 00:15:57.526
ober er iz nisht geven aktiv.

00:15:58.714 --> 00:16:00.918
ven di mame hot nokh gelebt,

00:16:00.925 --> 00:16:03.737
vi azoy hot zi gemakht

00:16:03.760 --> 00:16:06.623
shabes, yontev?

00:16:05.194 --> 00:16:08.563
bay undz iz gevezn, bay undz in der heym

00:16:08.113 --> 00:16:09.035
-huh.

00:16:08.788 --> 00:16:10.638
un in ale shtiber

00:16:10.830 --> 00:16:13.822
iz nisht geven keyn eyn shtub, keyn yidishe,

00:16:13.822 --> 00:16:15.763
velkhe zol nisht hobn

00:16:15.763 --> 00:16:18.451
fun ale yontoyvim, fun shabes.

00:16:18.542 --> 00:16:23.154
merer aktiv oder veyniker aktiv, veynik zey hobn gekent oder merer gekent,

00:16:23.154 --> 00:16:27.520
ober shabes hot men gehaltn. me hot gebentsht lekht. shabes.

00:16:26.000 --> 00:16:27.890
ale zaynen geven frum?

00:16:27.975 --> 00:16:28.745
a?

00:16:28.380 --> 00:16:30.433
ale zaynen geven frum?

00:16:30.557 --> 00:16:33.284
kimat ale, kimat ale.

00:16:33.493 --> 00:16:36.524
un ⟨um⟩ shabes iz men nisht geforn.

00:16:36.717 --> 00:16:39.023
shabes iz men geven in der heym.

00:16:39.062 --> 00:16:43.328
un me hot ge-, di oremste hobn gehat a shabes

00:16:43.328 --> 00:16:46.560
in di raykhere beser, farshteyt zikh, un azoy vayter.

00:16:46.560 --> 00:16:49.282
⟨nu⟩ in algemeyn iz geven genug oreme-layt,

00:16:49.339 --> 00:16:51.864
ober di yidn flegn helfn eyner dem andern.

00:16:51.955 --> 00:16:54.845
mir flegn ⟨UNK⟩ ⟨gebn di⟩ nedove, m'hot arayngrebrakht

00:16:54.845 --> 00:16:57.250
donershtik oder fraytik epes hilf.

00:16:57.250 --> 00:16:59.863
m'hot gezogt: got vet helfn, ⟨mistome⟩ vest opgebn,

00:16:59.869 --> 00:17:02.208
kedey me zol nisht farshemen dem mentsh.

00:17:03.075 --> 00:17:05.381
in toyznt nayn hundert akhtsn,

00:17:05.539 --> 00:17:09.400
az di mame iz geshtorbn, iz yedn tog keyn minyen nisht gevezn.

00:17:09.400 --> 00:17:11.878
nor fraytik oyf der nakht un shabes.

00:17:11.952 --> 00:17:14.547
hot mikh genumen der mame's a shvester

00:17:14.547 --> 00:17:16.249
in a shtetl Kosev.

00:17:16.575 --> 00:17:19.095
dos iz dos bakantste shtetl gevezn.

00:17:19.095 --> 00:17:21.196
gehat tsvelef toyznt aynvoyner,

00:17:21.196 --> 00:17:23.010
derfun zeks toyznt yidn.

00:17:23.010 --> 00:17:24.990
in Kosev iz shoyn gevezn a rebe.

00:17:25.300 --> 00:17:28.686
der rebe Hager, a dinastye fun tsvey hundert fuftsik yor.

00:17:29.080 --> 00:17:31.419
dos eyntsike hoyz in Kosev

00:17:31.459 --> 00:17:32.949
vos iz geven gemoyert

00:17:32.949 --> 00:17:35.401
un a groys hoyz, mit a groyser shul

00:17:35.644 --> 00:17:38.914
iz gevezn dem rebe's hoyz,

00:17:38.914 --> 00:17:41.597
vu s'iz gevezn oyfn ershtn FLOOR

00:17:41.597 --> 00:17:43.791
efsher tsvontsik gevelbn.

00:17:43.791 --> 00:17:45.729
er flegt fardingen di

00:17:45.786 --> 00:17:48.682
ROOMS far gevelbn.

00:17:48.840 --> 00:17:50.482
un

00:17:50.482 --> 00:17:53.745
mayn az mayn shvester hot khasene gehat

00:17:53.768 --> 00:17:56.574
keyn Kosev toyznt nayn hundert nayn un tsvontsik,

00:17:56.574 --> 00:17:59.105
hobn zey gehat afile baym, in rebe's moyer

00:17:59.105 --> 00:18:01.068
a gevelb hartvarn.

00:18:01.581 --> 00:18:03.476
un der rebe

00:18:03.476 --> 00:18:06.451
de- der der alter rebe

00:18:06.711 --> 00:18:09.675
iz geshtorbn in di tsvantsiker yorn.

00:18:10.288 --> 00:18:13.707
ikh hob gehat zeyer a interesantn tsufal.

00:18:14.760 --> 00:18:17.623
az ikh ⟨bin⟩ gekumen keyn Kosev zogn kadesh,

00:18:17.663 --> 00:18:21.757
bin ikh gevezn on, on eltern, ⟨a min⟩ a gut sheygetsl.

00:18:21.915 --> 00:18:23.967
fleg ikh nemen a sharf meser

00:18:24.244 --> 00:18:28.375
un ⟨ikh⟩ mayn mayn mame's shvester,

00:18:28.375 --> 00:18:29.486
der man

00:18:29.762 --> 00:18:33.792
iz gevezn, s'iz geven zeyer a shvere tsayt, geven a hunger

00:18:33.792 --> 00:18:36.104
bald nokh der milkhome, fleg er lifern

00:18:36.104 --> 00:18:40.506
kontrabande, umlegal, nisht vayt iz geven di grenets di rumeynishe

00:18:40.663 --> 00:18:43.031
lebn Viznits.

00:18:43.031 --> 00:18:45.140
Vizhnits iz shoyn geven rumeynish.

00:18:45.140 --> 00:18:52.857
un Kitev iz geven nokh fun der poylisher zayt. fleg er umlegal ariberlifern yede nakht a vagon mit kukuruzes, CORN.

00:18:53.067 --> 00:18:55.035
un dos hot gegebn parnose.

00:18:55.800 --> 00:18:58.359
un az ikh bin geven bay zey,

00:18:58.450 --> 00:19:01.298
hob ikh mit a meser oysgeshnitn di knep

00:19:01.298 --> 00:19:02.817
mit materyal

00:19:02.817 --> 00:19:04.519
fun di tayerste zakhn.

00:19:04.575 --> 00:19:06.729
men flegt makhn a yid an oyberrok,

00:19:06.972 --> 00:19:11.134
un der oyberrok iz shoyn geven oyf oyf a sakhn yorn, kimat oyf ⟨zayn gants⟩ lebn.

00:19:11.258 --> 00:19:12.889
ikh hob dos kalye gemakht.

00:19:12.912 --> 00:19:16.486
hot mikh der rebe, ge- der feter mayner Moyshe-Yosi Fuks

00:19:16.486 --> 00:19:19.183
genumen bay der hant un hot mikh gefirt tsum altn rebe.

00:19:19.408 --> 00:19:23.165
Kosev iz gevezn a lange gas eyne

00:19:23.442 --> 00:19:26.189
oyf oyf rekhts iz gevezn berg,

00:19:26.189 --> 00:19:27.975
oyf links a vaserl.

00:19:27.981 --> 00:19:31.302
un fun beyde zaytn di hayzer vos zaynen gevezn

00:19:31.302 --> 00:19:35.113
efsher tsvey kilometer, dos iz geven tsvelef toyznt mentsh vos zey hobn gevoynt dortn.

00:19:35.271 --> 00:19:37.189
hot er mikh gebrakht tsum altn rebe.

00:19:37.245 --> 00:19:39.950
er iz geven zeyer nervez, oyfgeregt.

00:19:39.950 --> 00:19:43.365
un gehaltn mikh shtark bay der hant, ikh zol nisht antloyfn, vayl ikh hob gekent antloyfn.

00:19:43.759 --> 00:19:47.013
zogt im der rebe: vos bistu azoy oyfgeregt, Moyshe-Yosi?

00:19:47.013 --> 00:19:48.174
vos iz mit dir?

00:19:48.535 --> 00:19:52.629
zogt er: ikh vel aykh bald dertseyln, vos er tut. un dertseylt vos ikh hob oyfgeton. zogt er:

00:19:53.142 --> 00:19:54.840
gib a kuk, Moyshe-Yosi.

00:19:54.913 --> 00:19:57.332
zayn tate gevezn a rebe

00:19:57.332 --> 00:20:00.004
in der estraykhisher armey un iz gefaln.

00:20:00.162 --> 00:20:01.871
di muter iz geshtorbn

00:20:01.871 --> 00:20:04.039
nayntsn akhtsn, zogt er kadish.

00:20:04.039 --> 00:20:05.589
iz er ⟨dokh⟩ a yosem ⟨to⟩?

00:20:06.186 --> 00:20:08.815
efsher in zayn zkhus, vos er zogt kadish,

00:20:08.815 --> 00:20:12.080
gelingt dir yede nakht aribertsufirn a vagon kukuruzes.

00:20:12.080 --> 00:20:14.131
dayne kinder geyen oyf peysekh

00:20:14.131 --> 00:20:16.794
fun vaysn layvnt a SUIT,

00:20:16.817 --> 00:20:18.026
a kostyum.

00:20:18.252 --> 00:20:22.341
vayl s'iz nishto keyn guter materyal, ober ⟨UNK⟩ nokh Peysekh

00:20:22.341 --> 00:20:24.135
mit yukhtene shikh gele.

00:20:24.360 --> 00:20:26.221
efsher iz dos in zayn zkhus?

00:20:26.221 --> 00:20:28.559
az vest im opshikn aheym un vet nisht zogn kadish,

00:20:28.559 --> 00:20:31.495
vet dir nisht gelingen tsu firn keyn vagonen mit kukuruzes.

00:20:31.495 --> 00:20:33.501
dos klugshaft fun dem rebe.

00:20:33.540 --> 00:20:35.055
khotsh ikh bin geven a kind,

00:20:35.055 --> 00:20:36.993
ken ikh biz haynt nisht fargesn.

00:20:37.202 --> 00:20:39.103
un ikh hob zikh oysgerisn

00:20:39.210 --> 00:20:40.469
un bin antlofn.

00:20:40.662 --> 00:20:44.515
a barg, vos me ken zikh nit aroyfkrikhn ahin, ikh bin aroyfgekrokhn.

00:20:44.515 --> 00:20:47.743
ober er hot genumen a faeton.

00:20:47.867 --> 00:20:50.437
un der balegole

00:20:50.437 --> 00:20:53.922
hot gegebn veynik tsu esn dem ferd, vayl er hot getrunken

00:20:53.922 --> 00:20:54.931
bronfn.

00:20:55.174 --> 00:20:58.863
iz dos ferd iz geven nebekh moger, vi Sholem-Aleykhem bashraybt.

00:20:58.988 --> 00:21:02.509
iz er gelofn, zogt er: for gikher, vayl s'iz avek mayn glik.

00:21:02.599 --> 00:21:04.663
akht kilometer bin ikh gelofn.

00:21:04.663 --> 00:21:07.774
un er hot mikh gekhapt in dem dorf, vi mayn mame ligt, Pistin.

00:21:08.185 --> 00:21:11.908
un dort hot er mikh shoyn gehaltn shtark un er hot mikh gebrakht tsurik.

00:21:12.049 --> 00:21:15.919
un hot gezogt der, der mame's shvester,

00:21:15.919 --> 00:21:18.112
Royze: s'iz nishto keyn tsuker,

00:21:18.112 --> 00:21:19.585
koyf im shokolad.

00:21:19.677 --> 00:21:22.373
farmakh im ⟨un⟩ hit, vayl az er vet antloyfn,

00:21:22.373 --> 00:21:24.162
vet antloyfn undzer glik.

00:21:24.162 --> 00:21:28.091
ot dos iz geven di khokhme fun dem Kosover rebe Hager.

00:21:28.165 --> 00:21:29.908
a hoykher yid,

00:21:29.908 --> 00:21:33.339
mit a bord vi Avrom-ovinu un mit a hoykher shtub

00:21:33.447 --> 00:21:37.170
fir meter ⟨iz⟩ di vent un arumgeleygt ful mit sforim.

00:21:37.395 --> 00:21:40.058
nor a kluger, a groyser goen.

00:21:40.058 --> 00:21:45.489
tsun im flegn kumen oyf di yontoyvim fun Ungarn, fun Tshekhoslovakay, fun Rumenyen khsidim.

00:21:46.052 --> 00:21:50.293
s'iz gevezn di, di ⟨badinen⟩, di yidn

00:21:50.293 --> 00:21:53.094
fun di religyeze oyffirer, fun di rabonim

00:21:53.094 --> 00:21:54.669
iz gevezn zeyer korekt.

00:21:55.485 --> 00:21:57.954
s'iz, in Poyln nisht ⟨UNK⟩ geven ongenem,

00:21:57.954 --> 00:22:02.094
az me darf, di rabonim hobn gehat funem kool

00:22:02.100 --> 00:22:06.009
a gevise gevise dotatsye fun gelt.

00:22:06.218 --> 00:22:06.873
nu,

00:22:06.873 --> 00:22:10.397
a rebe iz dokh nisht, iz er nisht ke-. a rov

00:22:10.470 --> 00:22:14.441
iz der vos er hot smikhe, pasket shayles, tsi s'iz treyf a hun,

00:22:14.441 --> 00:22:16.337
az me koylet ⟨un⟩ azoy vayter.

00:22:16.444 --> 00:22:19.290
ober rabonim zenen gevezn nisht azoy oft.

00:22:19.482 --> 00:22:22.277
Vizhnits, in Vizhnits iz geven ⟨a rebe⟩, in Kosev.

00:22:22.300 --> 00:22:23.880
in Kolomey.

00:22:23.903 --> 00:22:26.664
in Tshortkiv, in di groyse shtet azoy.

00:22:26.923 --> 00:22:31.692
azoy arum, az di di ale, tsum bayshpil, a rov

00:22:31.699 --> 00:22:33.853
hot gelebt zeyer basheydn.

00:22:34.163 --> 00:22:37.903
nor oyf shabes hot men gekent hobn a hun

00:22:37.943 --> 00:22:43.522
mit a yoykh, mit a kugl un azoy vayter, ober ⟨UNK⟩ hot men gelebt zeyer basheydn.

00:22:43.950 --> 00:22:47.221
un nisht gekukt deroyf iz gevezn zeyer

00:22:47.221 --> 00:22:48.720
freylekh dos lebn.

00:22:49.401 --> 00:22:51.977
di di yidn

00:22:52.050 --> 00:22:53.630
hobn tomed,

00:22:53.670 --> 00:22:57.072
di, afile, di vos zenen gevezn zeyer veynik bahavnt,

00:22:57.113 --> 00:22:59.976
hobn tomed farshtanen,

00:22:59.998 --> 00:23:02.388
az leshone-habo birusholaim.

00:23:02.715 --> 00:23:06.112
az dok-, s'iz, az s'iz do,

00:23:06.112 --> 00:23:09.004
s'iz gevezn aza Teodor Hertsl,

00:23:09.212 --> 00:23:10.972
velkher hot ongeshribn,

00:23:10.972 --> 00:23:14.718
velkher hot ongefirt mit mit onfirn

00:23:14.718 --> 00:23:17.256
vegn aynfirn tsiyonizm bay di yidn.

00:23:17.430 --> 00:23:20.279
di yidn hobn gevust, az tsu

00:23:20.279 --> 00:23:24.397
Erets-Yisroel darf men forn un me darf arbetn shver.

00:23:24.397 --> 00:23:30.775
deriber iz in Poyln geven ayngefirt, ⟨oyf⟩ me zol ⟨z-⟩ kenen forn keyn Erets-Yisroel,

00:23:30.775 --> 00:23:33.619
hot men gemuzt zayn tsugeveynt tsu shverer arbet.

00:23:33.619 --> 00:23:35.855
vayl in Erets-Yisroel iz nisht geven keyn tekhnik,

00:23:35.855 --> 00:23:37.522
me hot gearbet zeyer shver.

00:23:37.748 --> 00:23:39.530
iz HAKHSHARA,

00:23:39.604 --> 00:23:41.845
dos hot yeder KHALUTS,

00:23:41.845 --> 00:23:44.930
fun voser organizatsye er zol nisht geven zayn, fun MIZRAKHI oykh,

00:23:45.072 --> 00:23:47.920
gemuzt geyn af a yor-tsvey arbetn,

00:23:47.920 --> 00:23:50.544
un oyb di hent zenen gevezn mit mozelyes,

00:23:50.544 --> 00:23:54.409
iz a simen, az er ken arbetn af a shverer arbet.

00:23:54.409 --> 00:23:58.802
oyb er hot nisht gehat keyn mozelyes, iz a simen, az er iz nisht tsugevoynt tsu keyn shverer arbet.

00:23:59.027 --> 00:24:01.991
fun a shtetl geforn eyn mentsh.

00:24:02.487 --> 00:24:05.552
fun a dorf – zeyer veynik.

00:24:05.794 --> 00:24:09.427
un tsuzamen fun gants Poyln, fleg zikh tsuzamenmakhn a grupe

00:24:09.427 --> 00:24:12.268
fun tsvey hundert fuftsik - dray hundert mentshn.

00:24:12.375 --> 00:24:15.170
di England fleg gebn di sertifikatn.

00:24:15.345 --> 00:24:17.921
s'iz geven dortn farshidn di problemen.

00:24:17.944 --> 00:24:21.836
un di shtetlekh hobn ongefirt mit di derfer.

00:24:21.910 --> 00:24:25.965
di yidishe organizatsyes zenen geven zeyer ibergegebn.

00:24:25.965 --> 00:24:29.211
m'hot geshikt in di derfer mentshn, velkhe hobn gefirt SIKHOT.

00:24:29.217 --> 00:24:32.664
velkhe hobn gelernt, dertseylt di mentshn vegn

00:24:32.664 --> 00:24:35.457
di zigraykhe arbet fun di KHALUTSIM

00:24:35.457 --> 00:24:37.074
in di tsvantsiker yorn.

00:24:37.283 --> 00:24:40.351
Erets-Yisroel hot gehat di greste merheyt

00:24:40.351 --> 00:24:43.084
fun gute arbetorer

00:24:43.084 --> 00:24:47.430
in di felder, in Erets-Yisroel, fun Poyln, un dernokh

00:24:47.430 --> 00:24:49.691
veyniker fun di Rumenyen,

00:24:49.691 --> 00:24:52.093
un nokh veyniker fun Tshekhoslovakay,

00:24:52.099 --> 00:24:57.201
un mer veyniker oyf azoy fil fun Bulgaryen, fun Ungarn.

00:24:57.201 --> 00:25:01.037
di s- az se fleg avekforn en- fun a shtetl

00:25:01.110 --> 00:25:02.606
eyn mentsh,

00:25:02.612 --> 00:25:06.675
un di stantsye fun der ban iz gevezn tsvey kilometer,

00:25:06.675 --> 00:25:09.038
flegn zey geyn di shikh oyf di pleytses,

00:25:09.038 --> 00:25:10.942
zol nisht farporoshen di shikh,

00:25:10.965 --> 00:25:14.075
yung un alt flegn ⟨nebn⟩ der stantsye arumnemen zikh

00:25:14.075 --> 00:25:22.671
un tantsn dem freylekhn hoyre.

00:25:22.761 --> 00:25:26.332
m'hot getantst, flegn zogn di polyakn: vos far a min folk iz dos?

00:25:26.558 --> 00:25:29.786
zey lebn nisht ⟨azoy mer raykh⟩ un zaynen tomed freylekh.

00:25:29.786 --> 00:25:32.224
gib a kuk, me bagleyt eyn mentsh,

00:25:32.224 --> 00:25:34.027
un me makht aza min simkhe.

00:25:34.202 --> 00:25:37.402
un zey flegn ba- bavundern

00:25:37.493 --> 00:25:41.250
dem koyekh fun, fun di yidn.

00:25:42.184 --> 00:25:46.230
un, un kh'hob geendikt zogn kadish.

00:25:46.230 --> 00:25:49.586
ikh bin antlofn eyn mol fun, aheym,

00:25:49.609 --> 00:25:55.965
iz ⟨ober⟩ gekumen der feter, gebetn me zol mikh gebn tsurik, un ikh hob gezogt dem kadish. ikh bin geven a kleyner, me hot mikh geshtelt ⟨oyf a⟩ shtender.

00:25:55.971 --> 00:25:58.462
un der foter zayner, er fleg mikh oyshern.

00:25:58.755 --> 00:26:03.575
un nokhn yor bin ikh ⟨tsuge⟩geforn tsurik, nayntsn bin ikh geforn tsurik in dorf arayn.

00:26:04.003 --> 00:26:06.511
kh'hob gebenkt tomed aheym tsu di shvester.

00:26:06.906 --> 00:26:08.250
mit Rozen?

00:26:08.408 --> 00:26:09.178
ah?

00:26:09.488 --> 00:26:10.513
mit Roza?

00:26:10.585 --> 00:26:13.009
kh'hob gebenkt aheym tsu di shvester.

00:26:12.550 --> 00:26:12.877
YEAH.

00:26:13.335 --> 00:26:16.521
nu, s'hot zikh gevolt tsuzamen zayn mit zey.

00:26:16.521 --> 00:26:18.302
ikh hob fargesn tsu zogn,

00:26:18.302 --> 00:26:21.631
az in nayntsn fuftsn

00:26:21.840 --> 00:26:25.136
iz gevezn zeyer groyse kamfn fun der milkhome,

00:26:25.136 --> 00:26:29.431
un mir hobn zikh evakuirt keyn keyn Tshekhoslovakay.

00:26:29.431 --> 00:26:32.668
un dort hot Amerike gegebn produktn

00:26:32.691 --> 00:26:34.620
zeyer a sakh

00:26:34.620 --> 00:26:35.489
perl

00:26:35.489 --> 00:26:37.328
di kashes un azoy vayter.

00:26:37.328 --> 00:26:41.083
hot zikh geplodet shtark groyse shtsheres, vi, zaynen geven azoy groys,

00:26:41.083 --> 00:26:42.711
geferlekh. zey hobn zikh,

00:26:42.711 --> 00:26:46.821
zey hobn zikh, bay tog zenen zey arumgelofn. dos hot gebrakht tsun a groyser epidemye

00:26:46.821 --> 00:26:49.358
fun boykh-tifus bay di kinder.

00:26:49.583 --> 00:26:51.866
un zey hobn nisht gekent lokalizirn dos.

00:26:51.866 --> 00:26:54.211
iz vayl ⟨dos⟩ kind, s'iz gevezn krank,

00:26:54.211 --> 00:26:57.019
hot ⟨dos⟩ nisht shtark geratevet, ⟨me hot es⟩ ⟨UNK⟩ gesamt.

00:26:57.379 --> 00:27:01.932
der tate arayngeyendik in der milkhome, hot er gezogt der mame:

00:27:01.932 --> 00:27:04.866
zolst ophitn, er iz eyner geblibn,

00:27:04.922 --> 00:27:07.278
eyn yingl, finef meydlekh,

00:27:07.352 --> 00:27:09.016
az s'zol zayn a kadish.

00:27:09.748 --> 00:27:11.871
zi, di mame

00:27:11.871 --> 00:27:13.623
hot oysgefilt dem flikht.

00:27:13.984 --> 00:27:21.116
hot zi ge-, ikh bin geven krank oyf tifus, un az s'iz gekumen di doktoyrim mikh aveknemen, hot zi mikh tsugedekt mit a betgevant,

00:27:21.291 --> 00:27:23.664
un me genumen di s-, Maynkele un Sorkele,

00:27:23.704 --> 00:27:27.697
dermit hot men gemeynt, az ge- gezunte kinder, me vet in der fri zey opgebn.

00:27:27.771 --> 00:27:32.355
me hot di kinder, in der fri gegebn toyte kinder.

00:27:32.614 --> 00:27:34.363
ikh hob derfun nisht gevust.

00:27:34.825 --> 00:27:37.215
ikh hob dos nisht farshtanen, ikh bin geven a kleyner.

00:27:37.558 --> 00:27:40.263
ober ven ikh bin shoyn gevezn nit in Kosev,

00:27:40.263 --> 00:27:43.343
oyf dem ort, vu der tate iz geboyrn gevorn, Melnitsa,

00:27:43.343 --> 00:27:45.112
Tarnopoler voyevudtsve,

00:27:45.152 --> 00:27:48.487
un ba tsen yor hob ikh nokh ⟨nisht⟩ nisht geendikt di ershte klas,

00:27:48.730 --> 00:27:52.034
hobn zey mikh arumgenumen, zey hobn ale dray,

00:27:52.034 --> 00:27:55.001
vayl di tsvey hobn mer nisht gelebt. ⟨zey hobn⟩ mikh gut ongeshlogn.

00:27:55.176 --> 00:27:57.856
vos tustu? du lozst ⟨undz⟩ nisht lebn.

00:27:57.856 --> 00:28:00.471
bist a "midburenik." "midbure" iz a viste,

00:28:00.471 --> 00:28:01.447
midber.

00:28:02.044 --> 00:28:04.530
zay shoyn a mentsh! her shoyn oyf!

00:28:04.530 --> 00:28:06.394
du veyst, az durkh dir ⟨iz⟩ zgeshtorbn

00:28:06.394 --> 00:28:09.108
tsvey meydelekh, Maynkele un Surkele?

00:28:09.182 --> 00:28:10.830
az ikh hob dos derhert,

00:28:11.292 --> 00:28:13.075
bin ikh geblibn gepleft,

00:28:13.350 --> 00:28:15.487
ikh hob nisht gekent a por sho shmuesn,

00:28:15.696 --> 00:28:17.153
un ikh hob bashlosn

00:28:17.153 --> 00:28:18.981
tsu vern a gut yingele.

00:28:19.290 --> 00:28:20.764
dem andern tog

00:28:20.764 --> 00:28:22.305
hob ikh gornisht gezogt.

00:28:22.564 --> 00:28:24.788
kh'hob getun alts, kh'hob zey gefolgt.

00:28:24.788 --> 00:28:26.543
ikh hob ongehoybn tsu lernen

00:28:26.543 --> 00:28:28.948
un bemeyshekh fun eyn yor hob ikh deryogt

00:28:28.948 --> 00:28:30.720
in der hebreisher shul,

00:28:30.720 --> 00:28:32.430
in der yidisher shul,

00:28:32.470 --> 00:28:34.508
i- in kheyder

00:28:34.508 --> 00:28:37.172
ale ⟨mayne⟩ ⟨di vos zenen geven in mayn⟩ elter.

00:28:37.515 --> 00:28:40.749
un di, zey flegn far freyd veynen.

00:28:41.143 --> 00:28:44.160
s'hot mir gegebn a groysn veytik, az durkh mir

00:28:44.160 --> 00:28:46.959
zenen avek fun der velt tsvey shvesterlekh.

00:28:47.455 --> 00:28:48.076
un
